<form method="POST" action="/onboarding/ci_bot_account">
  <h4>2. CI Bot Account</h4>

  <p>
    <code>fastlane.ci</code> requires you setup a CI <i>bot account</i> to
    update the build status, etc.
  </p>

  <p>
    To properly setup the bot account, <code>fastlane.ci</code> requires
    two configuration envorinment variables: <code>FASTLANE_CI_USER</code>
    and <code>FASTLANE_CI_PASSWORD</code>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Please follow the steps below to complete your <code>fastlane.ci</code>
    cofiguration:
  </p>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <a href="https://help.github.com/articles/signing-up-for-a-new-github-account/">
        Create an account</a> for your <code>fastlane.ci</code> bot on GitHub.

      <p>
        <i>
          Note: it's important that you do not enable two-factor authentication
          for your bot account.
        </i>
      </p>
    </li>

    <li>Enter your bot user account email:</li>

    <div class="mdl-textfield mdl-js-textfield">
      <label for="input"><code>FASTLANE_CI_USER</code></label>
      <input
        id="ci_user_email"
        class="mdl-textfield__input"
        type="text"
        name="ci_user_email"
        value="<%= keys[:ci_user_email] %>"
        placeholder="your_github_bot_email@gmail.com"
      />
    </div>

    <li>Enter your bot user account password:</li>

    <div class="mdl-textfield mdl-js-textfield">
      <label for="input"><code>FASTLANE_CI_PASSWORD</code></label>
      <input
        id="ci_user_password"
        class="mdl-textfield__input"
        type="text"
        name="ci_user_password"
        value="<%= keys[:ci_user_password] %>"
        placeholder="Your GitHub bot's password"
      />
    </div>
  </ol>

  <input
    class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect mdl-button--accent"
    type="submit"
    value="Save bot account information"
  >
</form>

<!-- Progress to the next page -->
<form method="GET" action="/onboarding/initial_clone_user">
  <input
    class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect mdl-button--accent"
    type="submit"
    value="Next"
